The paper also involves runtime analysis and mathematical functions, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also deals with population size and segmentation, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
